gobblin.runtime.template

Class ResourceBasedJobTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.template.InheritingJobTemplate
      • gobblin.runtime.template.StaticJobTemplate
        • gobblin.runtime.template.HOCONInputStreamJobTemplate
          • gobblin.runtime.template.ResourceBasedJobTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JobTemplate, Spec, Serializable

    public final class ResourceBasedJobTemplate
extends HOCONInputStreamJobTemplate
    A JobTemplate that reads the template information from a resources file. This class is final because otherwise we could not guarantee the InputStream to be closed if the super constructor throws an exception.
